OL,3,CBill to scrap not proven verdict will
OL,4,Clead to 'clearer' system for Scotland
OL,6,FLegislation which will scrap
OL,7,FScotland's controversial not proven
OL,8,Fverdict will lead to a "clearer" and
OL,9,F"more transparent system, Holyrood
OL,10,FJustice Secretary Angela Constance has
OL,11,Finsisted.
OL,13,FThe measure is just part of a series
OL,14,Fof changes planned for the justice
OL,15,Fsystem as a result of a Scottish
OL,16,FGovernment Bill that is facing its
OL,17,Ffinal hurdle at Holyrood.
