OL,3,CBill to scrap not proven verdict will
OL,4,Clead to 'clearer' system for Scotland
OL,6,FScotland is the only country that has
OL,7,Fa not proven verdict ` with jurors
OL,8,Fable to find an accused person either
OL,9,Fguilty or not guilty, or that the case
OL,10,Fagainst them is not proven.
OL,12,FLike a not guilty verdict, it results
OL,13,Fin the accused person being cleared,
OL,14,Fhowever with the not proven verdict
OL,15,Fsaid to be used "disproportionately"
OL,16,Fin rape cases, campaigners against
OL,17,Fviolence against women have campaigned
OL,18,Ffor it to be abolished.
