OL,3,CBill to scrap not proven verdict will
OL,4,Clead to 'clearer' system for Scotland
OL,6,FIn addition to scrapping the third
OL,7,Fverdict, the Victims, Witnesses and
OL,8,FJustice Reform (Scotland) Bill also
OL,9,Fsets out to reform the jury process,
OL,10,Frequiring at least two thirds of
OL,11,Fjurors to support a conviction before
OL,12,Fsomeone can be found guilty.
OL,14,FThe legislation also proposes the
OL,15,Fcreation of a new, independent Victims
OL,16,FCommissioner and the establishment of
OL,17,Fa specialist sexual offences court `
OL,18,Fwhile also promising to give victims
OL,19,Fof such offences a lifelong right to
OL,20,Fanonymity.
