OL,3,CBill to scrap not proven verdict will
OL,4,Clead to 'clearer' system for Scotland
OL,6,FOther changes will see the Parole
OL,7,FBoard required to consider if killers
OL,8,Fhave provided information on the
OL,9,Fwhereabouts of their victims remains
OL,10,Fwhen considering if they should be
OL,11,Ffreed from prison, a move known as
OL,12,FSuzanne's Law after Suzanne Pilley,
OL,13,Fwho was murdered in 2010 but whose
OL,14,Fkiller has never revealed the location
OL,15,Fof her body.
OL,17,FWith more than 160 amendments tabled
OL,18,Fdue to be debated at Holyrood on
OL,19,FTuesday, MSPs will sit until late at
OL,20,Fnight considering the legislation.
