OL,6,FScottish Conservatives insist "common
OL,7,Fsense changes" need to made to the
OL,8,FBill before they will back it.
OL,10,FParty justice spokesperson Liam Kerr
OL,11,Fargued: "At the moment, it's a
OL,12,FVictims' Bill in name only ` a wasted
OL,13,Fopportunity.
OL,15,F"The Scottish Conservatives have
OL,16,Fsubmitted several common-sense
OL,17,Famendments to strengthen this bill and
OL,18,Fdeliver the real change that victims'
OL,19,Fgroups demand."
