OL,6,FHe said he welcomed the abolition of
OL,7,Fnot proven, as well as an earlier
OL,8,Fdecision by Scottish ministers to
OL,9,Fabandon plans to introduce judge only
OL,10,Ftrials for cases of rape and attempted
OL,11,Frape
OL,13,FBut Mr Kerr added that the Scottish
OL,14,FGovernment "must go further" in
OL,15,Fchanging the legislation otherwise
OL,16,Fministers will be "selling victims
OL,17,Fshort".
