OL,4,Clead to 'clearer' system for Scotland
OL,6,FTories want changes made to the Bill
OL,7,Fto bring about an inquiry into
OL,8,Fgrooming gangs in Scotland ` but also
OL,9,Fwant the legislation to be altered so
OL,10,Fthat victims are informed if someone
OL,11,Fis not prosecuted, or if a plea deal
OL,12,Fis agreed.
OL,14,FHowever the Scottish Justice Secretary
OL,15,Finsisted that if the "landmark Bill"
OL,16,Fis passed it will "transform the
OL,17,Fexperiences of victims and witnesses
OL,18,Fwithin Scotland's justice system".
