OL,6,FMs Constance said the changes would
OL,7,Fmean that "victims will be heard,
OL,8,Fsupported, protected and treated with
OL,9,Fcompassion" while at the same time the
OL,10,Frights of the accused "will continue
OL,11,Fto be safeguarded".
OL,13,FSpeaking about the proposals she
OL,14,Fstated: "Key reforms include
OL,15,Fabolishing Scotland's historic not
OL,16,Fproven verdict for a clearer, fairer
OL,17,Fand more transparent decision-making
OL,18,Fprocess.
