OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MSP Jamie Greene
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're so close to making the
OL,8,Fexperience of victims in the criminal
OL,9,Fjustice system a fairer and safer one.
OL,11,F"I have heard from so many people who
OL,12,Fhave been left not only devastated by
OL,13,Fthe initial crime, but also utterly
OL,14,Ftraumatised by how our system can tilt
OL,15,Ftoo far in favour of the perpetrator.
OL,17,F"My amendments seek to redress that
OL,18,Fbalance by introducing and
OL,19,Fstrengthening key protections for
OL,20,Fvictims and their families."
